<br />
There is also upgrade to CBS, it shares timer with other 2 nukes, but you can chain it every 3 sec as long as you don't use other instants. Trouble is it is 1537 mana. Think about it, this is outrage, 3.6 DPM is lower than any nuke we have. It means, in almost all situations, you are better off using Manaburn. Prathun is saying I don't want you using this!!!<br />
<br />
Kiting with 8.25 recast is a joke. We are going back to snare kiting without upgraded snare.</div>
